---
// Simple studio access page with consistent dark theme
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>EA Soft Lab CMS - Access Studio</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            background-color: hsl(230, 30%, 5%);
            background-image: 
                radial-gradient(at 20% 20%, hsl(210, 60%, 20%) 0px, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(at 80% 80%, hsl(240, 50%, 15%) 0px, transparent 50%);
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            color: white;
        }
        .container {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 500px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .container:hover {
            transform: translateY(-4px);
            box-shadow: 0 25px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }
        .button {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1 0%, #8b5cf6 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            display: inline-block;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.3);
        }
        .button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.4);
        }
        .button.secondary {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        }
        .button.secondary:hover {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
        }
        .success {
            color: #10b981;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .info-box {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1rem;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        }
        .tip {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        h1 {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1 0%, #8b5cf6 50%, #ec4899 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        ol {
            text-align: left;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
        }
        ol li {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        strong {
            color: white;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>üé® EA Soft Lab CMS</h1>
        <p class="success">‚úÖ Sanity Studio is ready!</p>
        <p style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);">Choose how you want to access your content management system:</p>
        
        <div style="margin: 2rem 0;">
            <a href="http://localhost:3333" class="button" target="_blank" style="font-size: 18px; padding: 15px 30px;">
                üöÄ Open Studio (Recommended)
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <div style="margin: 2rem 0;">
            <a href="https://easoftlab.sanity.studio" class="button secondary" target="_blank">
                üåê Web Studio (Coming Soon)
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="info-box">
            <h3 style="color: white; margin-bottom: 1rem;">üìã Quick Instructions:</h3>
            <ol>
                <li><strong>Recommended Studio:</strong> Click "Open Studio" to access your CMS locally</li>
                <li><strong>Login:</strong> Use your Sanity account to log in</li>
                <li><strong>Start Managing:</strong> Create and edit your content!</li>
                <li><strong>Web Studio:</strong> Will be available soon once deployment completes</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
        
        <div class="tip">
            <p>üí° <strong>Tip:</strong> The local studio is running and ready to use. Web studio deployment may take a few minutes.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
